attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate - All Seasons

data.description: Nice 3 bed, 1 bath, with 2 of the bedrooms on the main floor!  Full unfinished basement for extra living space waiting for your finishing touches. Kitchen has new counters, and the shingles were recently replaced!  Also there’s steel siding on this gem!  Don’t forget about the double garage providing ample storage space for your vehicles, tools, and outdoor equipment. Whether you are a car enthusiast or simply value the convenience of additional storage you will love the garage space with a heated & insulated workshop in the back! The backyard has fence on 2 sides, so it would be easy to enclose it for your family or pets! Close to the middle/high school, gas stations, ball parks, ice arena & more! Schedule your private showing today!
